## Component Usage

**Action components MUST be used in display components, not embedded.**

### ✅ Correct - Using Action Components

```typescript
import { AddCardButton } from './components/add-card-button';
import { EditCardButton } from './components/edit-card-button';

export function FlashcardList({ deckId, cards }) {
  return (
    <div>
      <AddCardButton deckId={deckId} />
      {cards.map(card => (
        <div key={card.id}>
          {/* Card display */}
          <EditCardButton 
            cardId={card.id} 
            front={card.front} 
            back={card.back} 
          />
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  );
}
```

